&lt;li&gt;Build and manage your own pipeline through existing relationships, networking events, and targeted outbound activity across email, phone, and LinkedIn Sales Navigator.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow up on inbound leads with speed and urgency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research and understand prospects&#39; business goals and KPIs to tailor presentations and commercial proposals to their specific needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the full sales cycle, from qualification calls and virtual demos through trial management, negotiation, and deal close, while ensuring a seamless handoff to Customer Success.&lt;/li&gt;
