&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABM Programs:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop and execute Account-Based Marketing (ABM) programs targeting high-priority segments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Event ROI:&lt;/strong&gt; In close collaboration with the Events team, coordinate lead generation activities for industry events and other field marketing activities.&lt;/li&gt;
